<br>
She kept herself sitting by the waters, although she liked to equal herself to everyone to try and keep titles out of things, this time she felt inferior to the Queen of the Gods. Perhaps it was necessary anyways for the festival, or perhaps it was just in Aly's own mind at the time.<br>
<br>
&quot;Everyday of my life Goddess.&quot;<br>
<br>
She sighed and looked skyward.<br>
<br>
&quot;I know that you often give guidance to the Themiscryan amazons, especially Hippolyte. But at this time, I am afraid I need it as well. Deeply.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 90<br> <font color=#993300>(6/21/01 3:38:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=160.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Assistance</span><hr size=1> &quot;Alysia,&quot; she spoke softly to the amazon.  &quot;I know that your world may seem confusing.  For you are trying to blend yourself..one from a warrior race..to that of a man of peace.  But, you must not forget that what it is in him that is so your opposite.. is much a part of why you do love him.  And as for him.. it is the same..your warrior heart...there is something there as well.&quot;<br>
&quot;Your northern amazon blood is much different than that of southern amazons.  Women whose ancestory at some time was connected to Ares.  Mayhaps, there is something in your people that is connected to the man of peace.  Your people were not originally born to be amazons.. or chose to leave the world of men to worship fully a Goddess and the way of amazons.  Your people were almost thrust into this life...with the lose of your men.&quot;<br>
Hera thought a bit after she said this.  &quot;Because your blood line does not come from Olympians...I really don't know what path to lead you.  But, mayhaps.. you should seek the Samsara within.  Try to understand who you and your people were before they chose to be amazons.  And this would mayhaps show you the light that is between your warrior heart and the heart of the man of peace.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=163.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=162.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=160.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=160.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.threadControl?topicID=160.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=160.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=160.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cells